data.description: Great one level home on a level lot with a flat fenced in backyard. Nice front porch overlooking the well maintained front yard.  The  level backyard features a nice concrete patio with a privacy fence and a storage building just off the driveway. Cute little 2/2 with a large laundry room just off the kitchen with potential to be an additional room. 2 car Garage for easy access and storage for this one level home. Seller is offering a 1 Year  Choice home warranty to the buyer to be paid for at closing. Seller improvements, New Ceiling Fans, New Attic Exhaust Fans(2), ReBuilt Double Garage Door, New Garage Exterior light, New Dishwasher, New Dining room light
